{"tid":1228984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《616書》","createTime":"2019-06-15T19:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T01:47:45.000Z","uid":107577,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"16f2c154ac0dbf5ec5a8aa7e758c1e62df679dc2","tid":1228984,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T19:28:53.000Z","msg":"《616書》<br />\n亮南伐，馬謖建言：「用兵攻心為上，攻城為下；心戰為上，兵戰為下」<br />\n<br />\n勝者，攻心為上，攻城為下。攻心者，兵不血刃，萬眾齊心。攻城者，扭轉六壬，五勞七傷。今上下一心，同仇敵愾，慎其言，盡其責，分而攻之，大略民心。既克，柒婦佈法緩之。<br />\n<br />\n唓，此援兵之計也！<br />\n<br />\n港府鄙，難測也，懼有伏焉。府腹背受敵，兵潰將散，苟延殘喘，不過一合之將。古有賢人曹劌曰：「夫戰，勇氣詞解也。一鼓作氣，再而衰，三而竭。彼竭我盈，故克之。」<br />\n<br />\n惜義士以死明志，眾人無不捶胸頓足，悲憤難平。唯大事未成，不宜節外生枝，自亂陣腳。宜力聚民心，上撤送中惡法，下撤義士惡刑。<br />\n<br />\n今成敗得失於一字，民心！得之長勝，失之必敗。問責一事絕非旦夕之間，來日方長，翼眾士然。<br />\n<br />\n今千載難逢之秋，望眾士摒棄前嫌，萬眾一心，何愁大事不成！<br />\n<br />\n身在海外，心繫吾港，朝朝憂心，夜夜難眠。<br />\n臨別涕零，唯曰：天佑吾港！"},{"pid":"f24770b6d1282e7cba82974291dcb6908eb2df8b","tid":1228984,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T19:32:34.000Z","msg":"好文好文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589790aa60581da2a0b4fec11e8fb4128c530f20","tid":1228984,"uid":248275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T19:32:49.000Z","msg":"Barvo"},{"pid":"5aed4cdba5ad3d688b94d8a8c779422f9d3c7b07","tid":1228984,"uid":248275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"589790aa60581da2a0b4fec11e8fb4128c530f20","tid":1228984,"uid":248275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T19:32:49.000Z","msg":"Barvo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T19:33:02.000Z","msg":"*Bra"},{"pid":"05470f514d9e52ac3dcf4787686f45266c22800c","tid":1228984,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T19:34:33.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504308df9a76372093da2b63f660d53416109dd0","tid":1228984,"uid":184132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T19:34:56.000Z","msg":"想跳想死嘅同我入一入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1228885\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1228885</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n全部人同我睇左佢"},{"pid":"1c07268a88eda3c0cf2f9959d2603c9442a94584","tid":1228984,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:20:38.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3139dcab0c66d5a4b5fbe2607fe632a4e4fa8c","tid":1228984,"uid":109609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:47:45.000Z","msg":"SKYRIM BELONGS TO THE NORDS!!!"}]}